channel.title: Secetweb.com - Launched
channel.description:
I'm proud to present: [img]http://secetweb.com/images/banner.gif[/img]
http://www.secetweb.com
I made website few days ago, it's gonna be SCAR script database. I have already collected about 50 scripts, all kind of categories. There is also Tutorial section, where I added all the best tutorials from moparisthebest. They are classified so it's easy to find what you are looking for!
In the downloads section, you can download things like:
[ul][li]Newest SRL[/li] [li]SCAR[/li][/ul]
SCAR scripts section contains allkind of scripts, they are also classified so it's very easy to find hat you are looking for.
I would be extremely grateful if you register and post your own SCAR scripts! (If you post someone else's script, please tell me who made it!)
For now, I allow unregistered users to shout on Shoutbox and comment on scripts. However, if it gets filled with non suitable material (aka spam) I will make it members only.
And the best thing comes here:
[ul][li]No adds :)[/li][/ul]
Looking forward!
-Secet
